Reed S. Lewis, Russell F. Burmester and Mark D. McFadden compiled andmapped the geology onto stable-base material;
Optronics Specialty Co., Inc. scanned the geologic map and providedminimally attributed Arc/Info interchange-format files to the USGS;
Pamela D. Derkey (USGS) imported the files, transformed them to UTM zone11 (with a y-shift) and attached and attributed an interim geologic mapdata model;
Thomas P. Frost (USGS) visually compared the hard copy plots with thesource;
Jon R. Oblad (EWU) annotated the point data for output at a scale of1:100,000.
